title: Beaverteeth
description:
Beaverteeth was a southern rock band featuring Rodney Justo on lead vocals. 
Fans of Atlanta Rhythm Section will know Rodney as lead singer on the first 
two ARS albums, before Ronnie Hammond filled the spot.Beaverteeth is rather similar 
to The Atlanta Rythym Section with whom they share many members.

Beaverteeth 1977 features Rodney Justo (ex-Atlanta Rhythm Section) on vocals. Though 
not very rocky (similar to A.R.S. soft tone all over), it's a really nice, 
playful album. 

Beaverteeth - Dam It 1978 is another album fromthe guys who used to be B. J. Thomas'
backup band not really a second album but more a continuation of the first.
